# Get your API key at: https://developer.riotgames.com/
# After registration, find your "Personal API Key" in the dashboard
#
# For production, we use 5 API keys for rate limit rotation (1800 requests per 10 seconds)
# Development: Use the same key for all fields below
# Production: Generate 5 separate keys for optimal throughput

